b'Accel World: Infinite\xe2\x88\x9eBurst: b'In 2046, many aspects of life are carried out on a virtual network. No matter how advanced the time becomes, however, bullying never disappears. Haruyuki is introduced to the "Accel World" and decides to fight as Kuroyukihime\'s knight.\n\n(Source: Official site)'
